These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
2 different games are played: canasta, poker
1. the person playing poker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Game   | poker | canasta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, oliveros
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
2. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Cigar   | davidoff | oliveros |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, comedy
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | romance |

 #################################

 
